Des filtres existent pour protéger cette application contre la consommation de données qu\'elle génère, mais nécessitent des ressources pour s\'exécuter.

Remarque importante - La combinaison spécifique de périphérique et de système d\'exploitation détectée ne permet pas au verrouillage de l\'écran de reprendre correctement lors de l\'exécution de ce logiciel. Pour configurer votre téléphone afin qu\'il revienne correctement une fois l\'écran verrouillé, accédez à Paramètres Android-> Verrouiller l\'écran-> Temps de verrouillage sécurisé sur \ "Instantanément avec la touche marche / arrêt ou lorsque l\'écran s\'éteint \" avant de continuer.

Remarque importante - De nombreuses versions du système d\'exploitation Android contiennent un problème où le système d\'exploitation est bloqué lors de la numérisation de fichiers multimédias (données cartographiques, vidéos). Nous avons détecté une version sur Android où nous pouvons résoudre ce problème en désactivant le processus \ "mediaserver \".

Déplacement de cartes et connaissance de la situation pour le système d\'exploitation Android

De nombreuses versions du système d\'exploitation Android contiennent un problème où le système d\'exploitation est bloqué lors de la numérisation des fichiers multimédias (données cartographiques, vidéos). Cela ne fonctionnera que sur certains appareils et systèmes d\'exploitation. Si vous décochez cette case, vous tenterez de restaurer l\'état d\'origine du scanner. Le scanner qui sera désactivé est le \'mediaserver\' et lorsqu\'il est bloqué, cela entraînera une décharge importante de la batterie.

Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network of via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.
This application requires the location permission to be set to \'Allow all of the time\'

Aby skonfigurować telefon tak, aby poprawnie powracał po zablokowaniu ekranu, przejdź do Ustawienia systemu Android-> Blokada ekranu-> Zabezpieczony czas blokady do \„Natychmiast po naciśnięciu klawisza zasilania lub po wygaśnięciu ekranu\” przed kontynuowaniem.

Ważna uwaga - wiele wersji systemu operacyjnego Android zawiera problem, który powoduje, że system operacyjny blokuje się podczas skanowania plików multimedialnych (danych map, filmów). Wykryliśmy wersję na Androida, w której możemy rozwiązać ten problem, wyłączając proces \"serwer mediów\" .

Ważna uwaga - system operacyjny Android próbuje wyłączyć funkcje, aby oszczędzać baterię, nawet podczas używania w scenariuszach operacyjnych.

Wiele wersji systemu operacyjnego Android zawiera problem polegający na tym, że system operacyjny blokuje się podczas skanowania plików multimedialnych (danych map, filmów). Działa to tylko na niektórych urządzeniach i systemach operacyjnych. Odznaczenie tej opcji spowoduje próbę przywrócenia oryginalnego stanu skanera. Skaner, który zostanie wyłączony, to \'mediaserver\', a jego zablokowanie spowoduje znaczne rozładowanie baterii.
Pokaż tradycyjną linię asocjacji między znacznikiem własnym a pożądanym punktem uderzenia.

중요 참고-Android 운영 체제는 운영 시나리오에서 사용 하는 동안에도 배터리 사용을 저장 하기 위해 기능을 비활성화 하려고 시도 합니다. 최적화를 사용 하지 않도록 설정할 것인지 묻는 메시지가 나타나면 * * YES * *를 선택 하십시오. 이렇게 하지 않으면 사용자 환경이 저하 됩니다.

Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network of via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.

Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.

Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network of via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.

Mapas en movimiento y conocimiento de la situación para el sistema operativo Android

Muchas versiones del sistema operativo Android contienen un problema en el que el sistema operativo se atasca al escanear archivos multimedia (datos de mapas, videos). Esto solo funcionará en algunos dispositivos y sistemas operativos. Desmarcar esto intentará restaurar el estado original del escáner. Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network of via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.

Use Your Location in the Background

ATAK asks for the ability to collect location in the background so that when users are running ATAK and background it to perform other activities, it can continue to report the precise location to team members either on a local network of via a TAK Server that the user has configured to use. The data is sent out to other team members to show the precise location of the individual helping with coordinating such things such as incident response, disaster relief, and personal safety.
\t1) This data is not sent to the developers of the application.\n\t2) ATAK does not collect location data when the app is not running, only when it is backgrounded.
